        },
        {
            "title": "華虹半導體上季盈轉虧 2024年盈利跌79.2% 料今季毛利率降至9%至11%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">華虹半導體(01347)公布，上季由盈轉虧，母公司擁有人應佔損失2520萬美元，主要因為外幣匯兌損失所致。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"華虹半導體官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/01347-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"華虹半導體官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/01347-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">華虹半導體官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">期內銷售收入5.39億美元，按年升18.4%；單季度毛利率11.4%，較去年同期提升7.4個百分點。上述兩者均符合指引，期內毛利達6143萬美元，較對上年度同期提升2.37倍。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">2024年度全年銷售收入20.04億美元，則按年減少12.3%，主要因為平均銷售價格下降，但部份被付運晶圓數量上升抵消。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">去年毛利率10.2%，較2023年度下降11.1個百分點。毛利2.05億元，按年跌57.9%；母公司擁有人應佔盈利5811萬美元，按年倒退79.2%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該公司又列出2025年首季指引，預計今季銷售收入約在5.3億美元至5.5億美元之間，按季下降1.7%至增長2%；預計毛利率將由上季的11.4%，降至今季約9%至11%之間。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14703864-%e8%8f%af%e8%99%b9%e5%8d%8a%e5%b0%8e%e9%ab%94%e4%b8%8a%e5%ad%a3%e7%9b%88%e8%bd%89%e8%99%a7-2024%e5%b9%b4%e7%9b%88%e5%88%a9%e8%b7%8c79-2-%e6%96%99%e4%bb%8a%e5%ad%a3%e6%af%9b%e5%88%a9%e7%8e%87%e9%99%8d",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/01347.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-13 16:50:24",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "全日收市｜港股收市倒跌  全日波幅787點  阿里急回小米倒跌逾半成",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股大幅波動，午升665點倒跌122點，阿里系、升幅顯著收窄，小米(01810)倒跌半成，友邦(01299)受追捧，部份內需消費股午後造好。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股6.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股6.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數全日收報21814點，跌43點或0.2%，今早開市報21958點，升100點或0.46%，午後一度急升665點或3.04%，隨即急回，約15:43開始倒跌，最低見21735，跌122點或0.56%，為全日低位。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股6.png.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股6.png.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：快手網站\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/bplib_20230713-103127_source-web_01024_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：快手網站\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/bplib_20230713-103127_source-web_01024_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 cla