6600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股6.png.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：快手網站\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/bplib_20230713-103127_source-web_01024_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：快手網站</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：友邦保險官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-171647__source-web_01299.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：友邦保險官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230914_FI_source-web_018103.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：小米官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：蒙牛乳業官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/20230719_FI_source-web_蒙牛乳業02319-2.png.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：蒙牛乳業官網</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數全日報5235，跌45點或0.87%，今早開報5321點，升40點或0.77%；</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生國企指數全日報8002，跌55點或0.69%，今早以8082點開市，升24點或0.3%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指全日收報21859，跌5點或0.023%，高水45點 ; 科指期貨報5235，跌52點或0.98% ; 低水3點; 國指期貨收報8017，跌53點或0.66%，高水14點。    </p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市成交1563.85億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">AI概念續推科網股升，快手(01024)升6.31%，報49.7元，為表現最佳藍籌股; 百度(09888)升5.74%，報94元，升幅居藍籌股第二位。4月1日起免費開放「文心一言」予大眾使用 ; 阿里巴巴(09988)升幅收窄至2.55%，報116.7元，成交居首 ; 騰訊(00700)收跌0.5%，報442元; 美團(03690)反彈2.9%，報159.7元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：快手網站\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/bplib_20230713-103127_source-web_01024_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：快手網站\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/bplib_20230713-103127_source-web_01024_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：快手網站</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">友邦(01299)急升，一度升幅居藍籌股之首，高見55.6元，收升5.42%，報54.5元，升幅居藍籌股第三位，公司完成120億美元股回購計劃，此外保誠(02378)公布考慮分拆評估 ICICI Prudential Asset Management Company Limited 上市的可能性，完成該項減持後，所得款項淨額擬回饋予股東。保誠全日升7.22%，報71.3元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：友邦保險官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-171647__source-web_01299.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：友邦保險官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-171647__source-web_01299.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：友邦保險官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">比亞迪系回調，比亞迪電子(00285)跌7.59%，報56元，為表現最差藍籌股及科指成份股，比亞迪(01211)收市跌幅擴大至3.69%，報339元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">連日揚升的小米(01810)急插，收跌5.57%，報41.65元，跌幅居藍籌股第二位 ; 聯想(00992)跌5%，報12.16元，跌幅居藍籌股第三位。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230914_FI_source-web_018103.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230914_FI_source-web_018103.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：小米官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">互聯網醫療股午後回順，阿里健康(00241)收升3.86%，報4.57元，升幅大為收窄 ; 京東健康(06618)升市僅升0.15%，報33.05元 ; 平安好醫生(01833)報6.24元，無升跌。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">消費內需股午後造好，蒙牛(02319)升2.75%，報15.68元 ; 華潤啤酒(00291)升2.46%，報25元 ; 百威亞太(01876)升1.22%，報7.47元 ; 李寧(02331)升1.14%，報16.04元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：蒙牛乳業官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/20230719_FI_source-web_蒙牛乳業02319-2.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：蒙牛乳業官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/20230719_FI_source-web_蒙牛乳業02319-2.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：蒙牛乳業官網</p>\n</a>\n</div>",
